===Etymology===
Coined between 1500 and 1510 from {{der|en|la|alacritās}},<ref>[http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/alacrity "Alacrity" in Dictionary.com]</ref> from {{m|la|alacer||brisk}} + {{m|la|-itas||-ity}}.

